{"tid":527048,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中六記得報billy mock","createTime":"2018-01-12T09:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T17:10:54.000Z","uid":120360,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"40a1edce91f5c8e8300a1a43ca8585f2e640a54b","tid":527048,"uid":120360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:12:16.000Z","msg":"又到咗一年一度DSE雞報mock嘅時間啦 <br />\n報咗Billy嘅我真係恭喜你啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收到收唔到真係完全靠彩數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收到嘅以為自己好好彩?唔好意思呀 評語都係得果雞碎咁少架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n經典重溫(上年架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ):<br />\n<br />\n近年不少文憑試(DSE)考生為更清楚個人強弱項，會在考試前報考補習社的模擬試(Mock Exam)，有考生在facebook群組投訴指，早前報考由一個導師提供的英文科模擬試後，對方疑「改唔切卷」，無寄回其中的寫作卷，令考生無法得知根據成績作出改善，在網上引起熱議。東網亦接獲多名學生的投訴，他們均擔心目前距離該科真正開考日子僅餘約10天，即使稍後取回試卷亦得物無所用。<br />\n<br />\n有網民早前在facebook群組「名校Secrets」以《$650報左(咗)個hea mock(敷衍的模擬試)》為題的貼文指，收回模擬試試卷後感到十分詫異，「佢(導師)連卷都未改晒」，不滿導師「收得學生既(嘅)錢，就已經係老師既(嘅)責任去俾翻一定既(嘅)水準學生，而唔係馬馬虎虎，hea(敷衍)左(咗)佢就算。」<br />\n<br />\n東網接獲讀者報料指，有關導師為任教於補習社遵理學校及英皇教育的Billy Ng(伍嘉朗)，但讀者至今仍未收到寫作卷，認為對方應在正式開考前3周將之寄回，「而家畀返都冇用啦，邊夠時間改善？」冀補習社「回水」。<br />\n<br />\n根據補習社遵理在網上刊登的廣告，導師Billy Ng(伍嘉朗)的英文科模擬試以「Super Mock Exam(超級考試)」作招徠，若以團購方式報考，每人650港元，而非團購價則為每人780港元，廣告指費用已包括3份試卷連「專業批改」、郵寄試卷，以及約3.5小時試後講解等。<br />\n<br />\n遵理發言人回覆時則指，事件是「一場誤會」。他表示在遵理報考有關模擬試的考生約有2000人，而寫作卷於上周五(24日)已寄回予考生，相信只是部分考生「未收到」，指3份試卷中其中2份卷早於上周一(20日)已寄回予考生，分開寄出試卷是希望「考生及早知某part(部分)成績，唔想拖佢哋」。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170326/bkn-20170326134900718-0326_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170326%2Fbkn-20170326134900718-0326_00822_001.html&d=ZLlp%2BqdNaSGF4Tu9lAAn4dZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=6946e4c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170326/bkn-20170326134900718-0326_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a5571597a189b3ed2f1460bb098c3198bf45b79e","tid":527048,"uid":120360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> push"},{"pid":"951e4a0e4c27a5d30c2f4c7f3f17458cdcd23b6e","tid":527048,"uid":159575,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"Hi Kris <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8caa542dd470ed12db710378ffac23dd204942f","tid":527048,"uid":120360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"951e4a0e4c27a5d30c2f4c7f3f17458cdcd23b6e","tid":527048,"uid":159575,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"Hi Kris <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T10:04:12.000Z","msg":"hi billy仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7cba9434db65ec9850026ea54b23c0f473ac285","tid":527048,"uid":34444,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"key word轉字煩膠數字標點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾billyNG你食屎啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"e61fff763284484d012754e228bf2ec443cfe693","tid":527048,"uid":11695,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"ci